						<summary>

						<p>East tier of the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> of Aivar temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Year 6: 977 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records a gift of ten <hi rend="italic">poṉ,</hi> for a perpetual lamp in the temple of Tiru-Aindaḷi-Mādēva at Koḍumbāḷūr in Uṟattūr-kūṟṟam by Tāḻi Śāttaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Rāśiṅgappallavaraiyaṉ for the merit of Tāḻi Aṟiñjigai. The <hi rend="italic">dēvakanmis</hi> received the gift. </p>						

